title: Divisional Round Recap: Vikings Walk-Off, Jags Shocker, Eagles Upset, Pats Roll (Football 01/15)
description:
Will Brinson, Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco, and Jason La Canfora break down a wild weekend of divisional round action and coaching news across the NFL. First, Will, Nick, Pete and JLC react to one of the best finishes in playoff history as the Vikings walked-off against the Saints. That's followed by a breakdown of the Jaguars' shocking road victory over the Steelers, the Eagles rousing defensive effort and upset of the Falcons, and the Patriots rolling to yet another AFC Championship Game.
